## Possible indicators

The module could calculate indices such as:

```text
Green View Index
Road Dominance Index
Sky Openness Index
Built-up Visual Pressure
Pedestrian Space Visibility
Hardscape Index
Vegetation / Road Ratio
Visual Comfort Index
Urban Grey Index
Street-Level Landscape Mosaic
```

Examples:

```text
Green View Index = vegetation pixels / all valid pixels

Road Dominance Index = road pixels / all valid pixels

Sky Openness Index = sky pixels / all valid pixels

Built-up Visual Pressure = building + wall + fence pixels / all valid pixels

Pedestrian Visibility = sidewalk pixels / all valid pixels

Hardscape Index = road + sidewalk + building + wall + fence pixels / all valid pixels
```

These indicators should be treated as visual/perceived indicators, not as objective land cover.

