## Relation to GTB / landscape mosaic thinking

The concept is somewhat analogous to landscape mosaic or pattern analysis, but from street-level imagery.

GTB / landscape mosaic style thinking:

```text
spatial pattern from top-down land cover
```

CVC StreetView GIS:

```text
visual pattern from human-view imagery
```

Possible analogy:

```text
top-down landscape mosaic:
forest / open land / water / built-up

street-level visual mosaic:
vegetation / road / sky / buildings / sidewalks
```

This could become a useful bridge between GIS, urban planning, landscape perception and computer vision.

