## 360° sector model

For 360° images, a useful first design could be 8 sectors:

```text
N
NE
E
SE
S
SW
W
NW
```

or numeric azimuth sectors:

```text
0-45
45-90
90-135
135-180
180-225
225-270
270-315
315-360
```

Each sector can receive its own semantic statistics.

Example table:

```text
image_id
point_id
sector_id
azimuth_from
azimuth_to
vegetation_pct
road_pct
building_pct
sky_pct
sidewalk_pct
terrain_pct
dominant_class
```

This would allow maps like:

```text
green view by direction
road dominance by direction
visual enclosure by direction
sky openness by direction
```

